"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 424px; height: 240px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Probability of response (defined as the absence of treatment failure) to ursodeoxycholic acid (UDCA) in primary biliary cirrhosis. Patients were randomized to UDCA (solid line) or placebo (dashed line) for the first 24 months and then all patients were treated with UDCA for the next 24 months. The probability of a beneficial response at four years was significantly higher in the patients treated with UDCA throughout the study.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
